'''棉籽油'''（{{lang-en|cottonseed oil}}）是從[[棉花屬|棉花屬]]植物種子提煉而成的[[食用油|食用油]]，主要來源為[[陸地棉|陸地棉]]和[[草棉|草棉]]，其植種用途在取得棉纖維、作動物飼料及榨油<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cotton.tamu.edu/cottoncountry.htm |title=Texas Is Cotton Country |publisher=Cotton.tamu.edu |date= |accessdate=2013-10-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021084716/http://cotton.tamu.edu/cottoncountry.htm |archivedate=2013-10-21 }}</ref>。

棉籽與其他[[植物油|油籽]]（如[[葵花籽|葵花籽]]）有類似的結構，由硬殼包覆著含[[油|油]]內核（[[種子|種子]]）。棉籽油使用在[[沙拉油|沙拉油]]、[[沙律#沙律醬|沙拉醬]]、[[蛋黃醬|美乃滋]]<ref name="cottonseed.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.cottonseed.com/publications/facts.asp |title=關於棉籽油的二十件事 |publisher=National Cottonseed Products Association |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017083204/http://www.cottonseed.com/publications/facts.asp |archivedate=2015-10-17 }}</ref>或[[洋芋片|洋芋片]]等零食，因為它[[香味|味道]]安定，不會掩蓋原味，遇熱不易起油煙<ref name="大統摻棉籽油">{{cite news |language= zh |title= 大量摻棉籽油 大統老闆「致富秘密武器」│大統油品涉造假 |url= http://udn.com/NEWS/NATIONAL/NATS5/8235047.shtml |author= 何炯榮、簡慧珍 |work= 聯合新聞網 |publisher= [[聯合報|聯合報]] |date= 2013-10-20 |accessdate= 2013-10-20 |archive-date= 2013-10-20 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131020190750/http://udn.com/NEWS/NATIONAL/NATS5/8235047.shtml |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

==成分==
[[File:Mississippi_Cottonseed_Oil_Company_seed_house.jpg|thumb]]]]
棉籽油一般含70％的[[不飽和脂肪酸|不飽和脂肪酸]]（18％的單元不飽和，52％的多元不飽和）、26％的[[飽和脂肪酸|飽和脂肪酸]]<ref name="USDA nutrient data764">{{cite web|url= http://ndb.nal.usda.gov/ndb/foods/show/764|title= Nutrient data for 04502, Oil, cottonseed, salad or cooking|publisher= United States Department of Agriculture|access-date= 2013-10-20|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130116215711/http://ndb.nal.usda.gov/ndb/foods/show/764|archive-date= 2013-01-16|dead-url= yes}}</ref>。完全[[氫化|氫化]]時則是94％的飽和脂肪酸和2％的不飽和脂肪酸（1.5％的單元不飽和，0.5％的多元不飽和）<ref name="USDA nutrient data627">{{cite web|url= http://ndb.nal.usda.gov/ndb/foods/show/627|title= Nutrient data for 04702, Oil, industrial, cottonseed, fully hydrogenated|publisher= United States Department of Agriculture|access-date= 2012-02-13|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130905114813/http://ndb.nal.usda.gov/ndb/foods/show/627|archive-date= 2013-09-05|dead-url= yes}}</ref>。

