url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150118162519/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/01/05/us-china-food-safety-idUSTRE80416P20120105 |dead-url= no }}</ref>，其以大豆油、棕櫚油、粗製棉籽油和違法添加的花生油[[香精|香精]]<ref name="杭报">{{cite web|language=zh-cn|title=广东作坊食用油销往全国添加棉籽油可能导致男性不育|url=http://zt-hzrb.hangzhou.com.cn/system/2012/01/05/011703983.shtml|author=郑莉娜|work=杭报在线|publisher=广州日报|date=2012-01-05|accessdate=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150118152709/http://zt-hzrb.hangzhou.com.cn/system/2012/01/05/011703983.shtml|archivedate=2015-01-18}}</ref>混入勾兌（調和）成花生油，並賣給「[[康師傅|康師傅]]」（[[頂新國際集團|頂新國際集團]]）在內等十多個品牌<ref name="永隆"/>。混充油銷售地區遍及廣東省[[深圳市|深圳市]]、[[東莞市|東莞市]]、[[佛山市|佛山市]]，[[廣西省|廣西省]]、[[湖南省|湖南省]]、[[江西省|江西省]]等地<ref name="杭报"/>。

2013年台灣爆發以低價棉籽油混充高價油的違法獲利事件，[[大統長基食品|大統長基]]<ref name="大統摻棉籽油" />和[[富味鄉食品|富味鄉]]<ref  name="富味鄉摻棉籽油">{{cite web |language= zh |title= 騙很大！富味鄉認了 24款內銷油摻棉籽油│富味鄉摻棉籽油 |url= http://udn.com/NEWS/NATIONAL/NATS4/8251553.shtml |author= 陳雨鑫、林宛諭 |work= [[聯合新聞網|聯合新聞網]] |publisher= [[聯合報|聯合報]] |date= 2013-10-25 |accessdate= 2013-10-26 |archive-date= 2013-10-27 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131027082025/http://udn.com/NEWS/NATIONAL/NATS4/8251553.shtml |dead-url= no }}</ref>進口粗製棉籽油加工後混摻入各種油品在國內販售。兩家業者的下游廠商高達100多家（大統）與1000多家（富味鄉）<ref>{{cite news |language= zh |title= 高雄揪出棉籽酚 加強檢驗、檢舉有獎│大統黑心油風暴 |url= http://udn.com/NEWS/NATIONAL/NATS5/8248869.shtml |author= 蔡容喬 |work= 聯合新聞網 |publisher= [[聯合報|聯合報]] |date= 2013-10-24 |accessdate= 2013-10-26 |archive-date= 2013-10-27 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131027075309/http://udn.com/NEWS/NATIONAL/NATS5/8248869.shtml |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language= zh |title= 富味鄉下游廠商 多達1034家、分布19縣市 |url= http://iservice.libertytimes.com.tw/liveNews/news.php?type=%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB&no=890387 |author=  |work= 自由電子報 |publisher= [[自由時報|自由時報]] |date= 2013-10-26 |accessdate= 2013-10-26 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131029185458/http://iservice.libertytimes.com.tw/liveNews/news.php?type=%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB&no=890387 |archivedate= 2013-10-29 }}</ref>，影響遍及全台。富味鄉外銷油品販售至[[香港|香港]]、[[新加坡|新加坡]]、[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]、[[澳洲|澳洲]]、[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]、[[加拿大|加拿大]]等地，棉籽油混充比率最高達95％<ref>{{cite news |language= zh |title= 富味鄉外銷2款油 95％棉籽油 |url= http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2013/new/oct/23/today-t1.htm?Slots=All |author= 吳為恭、劉曉欣、賴筱桐 |work= 自由電子報 |publisher= [[自由時報|自由時報]] |date= 2013-10-23 |accessdate= 2013-10-26 |archive-date= 2013-10-29 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131029183932/http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2013/new/oct/23/today-t1.htm?Slots=All |dead-url= no }}</ref>。更且，棉籽油渣餅（cottonseed cake）進口量從150公斤暴增到5559公噸，由於[[農委會|農委會]]未有效檢查及管理而去向不明，若成為餅乾原料甚至是拿來榨油，將擴大危害層面<ref>{{cite news |language= zh |title= 棉籽油渣餅 5500噸流向不明 |url= http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2013/new/oct/26/today-t1-2.htm?Slots=T |author= 張傳佳、鍾麗華、林詩萍 |work= 自由電子報 |publisher= [[自由時報|自由時報]] |date= 2013-10-26 |accessdate= 2013-10-26 |archive-date= 2013-10-26 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131026003637/http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2013/new/oct/26/today-t1-2.htm?Slots=T |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language= zh |title= 棉籽油渣餅進口量增孫璐西：確實異常 |url= http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20131025/281112/ |author= 邱俊吉 |work=  |publisher= [[蘋果日報|蘋果日報]] |date= 2013-10-25 |accessdate= 2013-10-26 |archive-date= 2015-09-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150924135525/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20131025/281112/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。棉籽油進口量大統長基佔4成<ref>{{cite news |language= zh |title= 食藥署滅火！「精煉棉籽油」可下肚　工業油做QQ香皂 |url= http://www.ettoday.net/news/20131023/285520.htm |author=  |work= ETtoday 新聞雲 |publisher=  |date= 2013-10-23 |accessdate= 2013-10-23 |archive-date= 2013-10-25 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131025170356/http://www.ettoday.net/news/20131023/285520.htm |dead-url= no }}</ref>，富味鄉佔6成<ref>{{cite news |language= zh |title= 棉籽油 6成流向富味鄉 |url= http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/headline/20131022/35381618/ |author=  |work=  |publisher= [[蘋果日報|蘋果日報]] |date= 2013-10-22 |accessdate= 2013-10-23 |archive-date= 2013-10-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131024061922/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/headline/20131022/35381618 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

==用途==
工業上棉籽油大多是[[肥皂|肥皂]]、[[蠟燭|蠟燭]]和[[化妝品|化妝品]]原料，或成為汽車的[[生質燃料|生質燃料]]<ref>{{cite news |language= zh |title= 棉籽油含棉酚 殺精且亂經 |url= http://news.sina.com.tw/article/20131021/10914196.html |author=  |work= 新浪新聞中心 |publisher= [[民視新聞|民視新聞]] |date= 2013-10-21 |accessdate= 2013-10-22 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131029195627/http://news.sina.com.tw/article/20131021/10914196.html |archivedate= 2013-10-29 }}</ref>。或是做為機器的[[潤滑劑|潤滑劑]]「針車油」。

在農業方面，棉籽油的毒性可被認為對殺蟲是有益的：包括植物油在內的各種油脂，已經數百年來當作[[殺蟲劑|殺蟲劑]]用在控制昆蟲和蟎類害蟲<ref name=CSU>W.S. Cranshaw and B. Baxendale, Colorado State University Extension.  Updated Friday, April 19, 2013 [http://www.ext.colostate.edu/pubs/insect/05569.html Insect Control: Horticultural Oils] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ext.colostate.edu/pubs/insect/05569.html |date=20131104080116 }}</ref>。棉籽油普遍被認為是最殺蟲的植物油<ref name=CSU/>。

傳統上棉籽油用在[[薯片|薯片]]等食品，為{{tsl|en|Crisco}}起酥油的主要原料<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.crisco.com/Products/Details.aspx?groupID=17&prodID=803 |publisher=crisco.com |title=Ingredient facts |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091115070325/http://www.crisco.com/Products/Details.aspx?GroupID=17&ProdID=803 |archivedate=2009-11-15 }}</ref>。但由於棉籽油比[[橄欖油|橄欖油]]或[[芥花籽油|芥花籽油]]顯著便宜（每公斤低於25元新台幣<ref name="傷害精蟲" />），而開始廣泛使用在[[糧食|糧食]]、[[麵包|麵包]]、[[零食|零食]]、[[人造奶油|人造奶油]]等方面的[[加工食品|加工食品]]上<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cotton247.com/cg/?storyid=743 |publisher=cotton 247.com |title=Cottonseed oil use on the rise |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708194121/http://www.cotton247.com/cg/?storyid=743 |archivedate=2011-07-08 }}</ref>。

